SSL
=======

This module configures SSL.
It has been developed under Ubuntu 10.04.

It is able to setup:
- install and configure SSL
- install certificates, keys, certificate chains
- create configuration snippets suitable for apache2, openvpn, cyrus

Conventions
-----------
This modules is making user of standard Debian/Ubuntu conventions, aka certs will be placed in the standard folder,
use of update-ca-certificates command.

Dependencies
------------

* Concat git://github.com/ripienaar/puppet-concat.git

